@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Home Page";
}

<div class="text-center">
    <h1 class="display-4 s1">Welcome to Our Blog</h1>
    <h3 class="s2">Stay curious. Explore insightful stories from our writers.</h3>
    <a href="/Account/home" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Start Reading</a>

    <!-- Additional Content Sections -->
    <section class="mt-5">
        <h2 class="mb-4">About Our Blog</h2>
        <p>Welcome to our blog, where we aim to provide you with engaging and thought-provoking content on a wide range of topics. Our writers are passionate about sharing their knowledge and insights, covering everything from technology and science to lifestyle and culture.</p>
        <p>Our mission is to inspire curiosity and foster learning through our articles, essays, and opinion pieces. Whether you're looking for informative guides, personal stories, or in-depth analysis, you'll find it all here.</p>
        <p>Join us on a journey of discovery as we explore the world through the written word.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-5">
        <h2 class="mb-4">Why Choose Us?</h2>
        <p>With so many blogs out there, you might be wondering why you should choose ours. Here are a few reasons:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Quality Content: We prioritize quality over quantity, ensuring that each post offers value to our readers.</li>
            <li>Diverse Perspectives: Our writers come from diverse backgrounds, offering unique insights and viewpoints on various topics.</li>
            <li>User-Friendly Experience: Our website is designed to be intuitive and easy to navigate, allowing you to find the content you're interested in quickly and easily.</li>
            <li>Engaging Community: We believe in fostering a supportive and engaged community of readers and writers, where everyone's voice is heard and respected.</li>
            <li>Regular Updates: We publish new content regularly, so there's always something fresh and interesting to read.</li>
        </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-5">
        <h2 class="mb-4">Get Involved</h2>
        <p>Interested in contributing to our blog? We're always looking for talented writers to join our team. Whether you're an experienced journalist or a passionate hobbyist, we welcome contributions from writers of all backgrounds and skill levels.</p>
        <p>If you have a story to share or an idea for an article, we'd love to hear from you. Get in touch with our editorial team to learn more about how you can become a part of our community.</p>
    </section>
</div>

